<body>
To be approved by an Immortal or an Avatar,<br>
you must have the following:<br>
<br>
An acceptable name - see help Names<br>
An appearance - see help Appearance<br>
A list of keywords - see help Keywords<br>
A description - see help Description<br>
<br>
Use the identity command to see your keywords and appearance.<br>
<br>
You must be approved to advance to level 6.<br>
Please read all the help files and follow their guidelines to get<br>
approved.  Approvals are very time consuming and we ask for your<br>
cooperation.<br>
<br>
When you are ready for approval type: request avatar approval<br>
Type who to see if any avatars are currently on.<br>
Avatars will have AV by their names on the who list.<br>
   <br>
Finally, please take your time, read the help files that govern how<br>
appearances and descriptions should look, and see if you can come up with<br>
one that knocks people's woolen socks off.<br>
<br>
Once you are approved, please type: request cancel to remove your<br>
request from the queue.<br>
</html>
</body>
